This an impressive fast food Indian restaurant on line with chipotle. There are indoor and outdoor seating in this self service restaurant. Ordering is easy and the menu is not overwhelming. One can order a bowl, salad or sandwich in addition to the bbq. The place is very clean. The cooking area is behind glass door and visible. Eeny meeny miny moe are 4 huge clay oven for tandoor. 

Prices are reasonable for the quality and definitely for the quantity. The food is not spicy at all. The chicken biryani is tasty made of basmati rice and chicken is well marinated and succulent. The chicken tikka masala bowl is delicious. The Channa masala bowl was ok.

For dessert the malai kulfi is a must try.